<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">How it works</h3>

<p class="govuk-body">
  Behind the scenes, the Translate this Page feature:
</p>

<ol class="govuk-list govuk-list--number">
  <li>Extracts the main content from the page (preserving HTML structure)</li>
  <li>Automatically detects the source language (usually English)</li>
  <li>Sends the content to AWS Translate via a secure API</li>
  <li>Receives the translated content and replaces the page text</li>
  <li>Caches translations for faster repeat visits</li>
</ol>

